.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, drawing
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, aquamarine
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, german
2 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse
2 different games are played: snooker, whist
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the owner of the mouse is the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the german is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | iced-tea |
| Hobby         | drawing        | dancing  |
| Color           | blue | aquamarine  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Nationality   | australian     | german   |
| Pet           | lizard         | mouse    |
| Game     | snooker           | whist      |

